          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Yammy, we believe that clean food starts with transparency. Here's what you need to know about lead levels in our sweet potatoes.</p><p>Lead is a naturally occurring element in the Earth’s crust (found in soil, water, and air everywhere on the planet), and as a root vegetable, it is very difficult for any sweet potato product to have \"zero\" lead. The goal is to source from soil that has the lowest possible background levels.</p>",
